The Mesen adapter has two license boundaries:

- Runtime Lua (`emucap-core.lua` and the per-system entry scripts) is loaded as
  a separate script and is licensed GPL-2.0-or-later, the project default.
- `patches/*.patch` modifies and is compiled into MesenCE. That patch stack is a
  derivative of MesenCE and is licensed GPL-3.0-or-later.

The repository distributes pinned source patches and build recipes, not Mesen
binaries. See ../../NOTICE.

